name: Introvert Coin
description: $INTROVERT is a meme coin built on Solana that channels the humor, culture, and energy of one of the largest male meme communities on X. The project represents a satirical take on “introvert culture,” blending social commentary with viral internet humor. While primarily entertainment-driven, $INTROVERT aims to cultivate a tight-knit community of like-minded holders through content, engagement, and meme-based campaigns.
